  <title>IlmBase-&ilmbase-version;</title>

  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction</title>

    <para>
      The IlmBase package provides a set of utility libraries released by
      Industrial Light &amp; Magic and used by OpenEXR.
    </para>

